com.ingenico.connect.gateway.sdk.java

Class Communicator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ingenico.connect.gateway.sdk.java.Communicator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    LoggingCapable, Closeable, AutoCloseable

    public class Communicator
extends Object
implements Closeable, LoggingCapable
    Used to communicate with the GlobalCollect platform web services.

    It contains all the logic to transform a request object to a HTTP request and a HTTP response to a response object.

    Thread-safe.
